overview: Low-budget science fiction. A video piece full of special flaws and a lot of creepy tape. Vaginal Panic narrates the trajectory of a superheroine who opts for Intimate Weaponry - A procedure that can be installed in the vaginal or anal canal: pistols, shotguns, rifles, rifles, machine guns - All hypoallergenic and also available in pink, purple versions and gliterized.
title: Pânico Vaginal
